Finally the Foam World Tour will be bringing all the excitement of Cancun Ibiza to Down Town Houston For the first time ever Downtown will be the host to an exclusive UP Foam party If you have never been to a Foam party it is definitely an experience that you will never forget You may have seen footage from MTV or EEntertainment TV but to experience FOAM is like no other clubbing experience The FOAM used will be a dry airbased foam that is neither sticky nor harmful We will also have towels a coat check on hand for your convenience Be apart of the vibe that is sweeping dancefloors from
